html.body: ONTOX_LL0003_001 Fatty Acids and Cholesterol Transport This model was constructed integrating the Fatty acid transporters (Homo sapiens) metapathway (WP5061), the Cholesterol metabolism (Homo sapiens) (WP5304) and the KEGG Cholesterol metabolism pathway (map04979) as well as information from the literature.
